br.com.rafaelns.enums

Enum Direction

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Direction>
      • br.com.rafaelns.enums.Direction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Direction> 

    public enum Direction
extends java.lang.Enum<Direction>
    Represents the Direction that the Robot can face and walk.

    The Direction has three properties.

    • angle its used internally to determine what Direction is the next clockwise or counter clockwise.
    • incrementBy its used to know if it Direction increase or decrease the position on the Axis
    • axis its used to inform what Axis that Direction can interact with

    Have a look at Axis if needed.
